Stromae is a singer-songwriter of Belgian-Rwandan origin. He became famous "overnight" in 2009 when the music manager of NJR aired his first single. In a matter of weeks the sales of the album rose to number one in Belgium, and by May 2010 it reached number one in several countries. 
At TEDx Brussels he presented the procedure of the building up of his songs.

@TEDxBrussels 2010
